<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> kopparakecaripa<hi rend="grantha">nma</hi> ṟku yāṇṭu <num value="10"><g type="numeral">10</g></num> Āvatu tiruneyttāṉattu <hi rend="grantha">ma hāde-</hi> varkku naṉtinallūruṭaiyāṉ Āruraṉ kūttaṉāṉa <unclear>mī</unclear>ṉavaṉ viḷat
<lb n="2" break="no"/>tūrnāṭṭukkoṉ Ivvūr <hi rend="grantha">śrīkārya</hi> mārāyāniṟkka Ivvūr Aṅkāṭiyil Ūrāḷvarkaḷ peṟu maṅkāṭikkūli koṇṭu Ivvūr nakaravāriyañ ceyavomme
<lb n="3" break="no"/>y nicatam Uḻak keṇṇaiy ca<hi rend="grantha">ndrā</hi> titaval Oru nontāviḷak kerikka Aṭṭuvo(m)māṉom Ivvūr nakaravāriyañ ceyvom Itu <hi rend="grantha">panmā heśvara rakṣai <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied></hi> 
</p>

